E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1506','6','沈阳','中国嘉鱼网','<p><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><st1:chsdate w:st=\\\\\"on\\\\\" isrocdate=\\\\\"False\\\\\" islunardate=\\\\\"False\\\\\" day=\\\\\"20\\\\\" month=\\\\\"4\\\\\" year=\\\\\"2012\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 4</span>月<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">20</span>日</st1:chsdate>，县长余珂、副县长李德炳一行对嘉鱼甘泉水业公司进行了实地调研。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\\\\\">余珂一行先后到自来水收费大厅、石矶头水厂、污水处理厂等地进行了实地察看，并在污水处理厂召开了座谈会，听取了相关负责人的情况汇报，了解我县城区供水实际情况。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\\\\\">余珂说，自来水行业是直接关系到民生的重要行业，甘泉水业公司要不断加大对供水管网改造的力度，加快对城区老管网维修改造的进程，提高城区供水质量、提高污水处理水平。他指出，对于改公司目前遇到的实际问题，县政府将召开会议研究解决。该由政府支持的，县委县政府一定不遗余力进行支持；该由企业自己承担的义务和责任，企业也必须严格履行职责。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\\\\\">余珂强调，甘泉水业公司作为县城区唯一供水企业，要从群众的要求和企业的发展出发，做好应对各种突发情况准备，防患于未然，真正做到让县委、县政府放心，让广大人民群众满意。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\\\\\">县住建局局长尹彬生陪同调研。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1507','6','杨利','中国嘉鱼网','<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2012-04-22/21a752c3fde1264999bcfcb1cf8311db.jpg\\\\\" /><br />\r\n<span style=\\\\\"font-size: medium\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">冯家清一行在二乔公园参观</font></span></div>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><st1:chsdate w:st=\\\\\"on\\\\\" isrocdate=\\\\\"False\\\\\" islunardate=\\\\\"False\\\\\" day=\\\\\"20\\\\\" month=\\\\\"4\\\\\" year=\\\\\"2012\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">4</span>月<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">20</span>日</st1:chsdate>，省住建厅城市管理处处长冯家清来我县检查城市管理工作。咸宁市城市管理局长孙新淼，县长余珂，副县长李德炳陪同检查。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\\\\\">冯家清一行先后参观了政府广场、二乔公园、环湖景观带、山湖温泉等地。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\\\\\">冯家清对我县在城市管理工作中大力改善城市环境、不断提升城市综合管理水平等方面的新成效给予高度肯定。他说嘉鱼邻江含湖、依山傍水，是一个别具特色的山水园林城市，生态环境得天独厚。下一步，嘉鱼县城市规划和管理工作要向市级城市、省会城市看齐，城市规划要提高标准、更加精细化，全力塑造市容整洁、功能齐全、设施配套、环境优美、文明有序的现代城市形象。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\\\\\">县规划执法局局长何晓山、县住建局局长尹彬生陪同检查。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1508','6','熊铁山','中国嘉鱼网','<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2012-04-23/0b31a1221211d9d25aed890a3b2d9442.jpg\\\\\" /><br />\r\n会议现场<br />\r\n</font></span></div>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">4</span>月<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">23</span>日，省委常委、省纪委书记侯长安来我县调研纪检监察机构派出改革工作。市领导黄楚平、龙良文、王远鹤、夏亚灵，县领导熊征宇、魏朝东陪同调研。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">侯长安对我县纪检监察机构派出改革工作给予充分肯定。他说，嘉鱼县纪检监察机构派出改革工作有成效、有特色、有创新。近八年的实践，在案件监察、信访调查、监督检查等方面的作用非常明显，趟出了一条路，为全省纪检监察机构派出改革积累了经验、作出了贡献。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">他强调，纪检监察机构派出改革要继续坚定信心，明确目标；要坚定进一步深化纪检监察机构派出改革的信心不动摇、不徘徊；要继续坚持改革和探索；要科学设定改革方案，完善工作机制、运行机制、干部管理机制，配齐配强人员，探索派出机构更为有效的监督办法，提高工作实效；要注重总结，完善制度。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">县委书记熊征宇汇报了嘉鱼县纪检监察机构派出改革情况。从<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2004</span>年底开始，我县探索启动纪检监察机构派出改革；<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2005</span>年<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">1</span>月，率先在全省实施派驻纪检组统一管理模式试点工作；<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2008</span>年<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">6</span>月，按照省纪委的要求，对纪检监察机构探索实行分类改革。下一步，嘉鱼县委将继续全力支持纪检监察部门深化改革工作，重点在加强队伍建设、提供后勤保障、支持案件查办等方面做好坚强后盾。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">省纪委副书记余幼明主持会议。嘉鱼县纪委派出纪检组长、部分派驻纪检组长和相关单位负责人做了交流发言。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><o:p><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1509','6','刘蒙、鲁辉','中国嘉鱼网','<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2012-04-23/30ccce33513823f3a858653cb4faa728.jpg\\\\\" /><br />\r\n</span></font></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\\\\\">会议现场<br />\r\n</span></font></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2012-04-23/d6ad9e41a4b50a1dc3f3915cfd26b610.jpg\\\\\" /></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 16px\\\\\">余珂给化工协会会长授牌</span></div>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; text-align: left; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">4</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\\\\\">月</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">23</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\\\\\">日，县委、县政府在汉举办了湖北嘉鱼化工协会成立暨嘉鱼潘湾畈湖工业园招商大会。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">146</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\\\\\">家化工企业负责人参会，</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">10</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\\\\\">家化工企业与潘家湾镇现场签约，协议投资额达</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">3.8</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\\\\\">亿元。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\\\\\">嘉鱼县潘湾畈湖化工工业园是我县积极承接武汉城市圈及长三角、珠三角化工产业转移，推进工业经济与招商引资的一项重要举措。园区占地</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">4</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\\\\\">平方公里，已进入第四期和第五期建设阶段，将完成固定资产投资</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">15</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\\\\\">亿元。目前已引进精细化工企业</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">65</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\\\\\">家入驻园区，其中</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">18</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\\\\\">家落成投产。潘家湾镇党委书记周亚澜说，该园区作为市级化工园区，正在创建省级工业园区，计划在三年内实现&ldquo;入园企业</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">100</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\\\\\">家，园区产值</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">50</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times N