argin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">培训采取专题讲座、典型报告、实地参观、交流讨论等方式进行。培训内容主要围绕加强农村基层组织建设、农村社会管理和维稳工作现状与对策、&ldquo;十二五&rdquo;发展规划、十七届六中全会精神解读、发展壮大村级集体经济、农村党建工作、农村经济社会发展等方面。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">&ldquo;八组的奋斗历程令人感慨！我将把此次培训的收获和感悟带回去，坚定不移的带领群众干起来、强起来、富起来</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">!</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">&rdquo;实地参观官桥八组后，大冶市还地桥镇黄金湖村党支部书记余德明感慨的说。</span><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\"> <span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-prop-change: 微软用户 20120424T0833\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">据悉，为了加强周边县市的交流和合作，嘉鱼县积极协助做好黄石市、鄂州市农村党组织书记培训工作，此举是积极构建&ldquo;</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">1+8</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">&rdquo;城市圈的具体体现。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\" size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1520','6','熊铁山','中国嘉鱼网','<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2012-04-24/4433323300b7d50a203968452bc69470.jpg\\\\\" /><br />\r\n会议现场<br />\r\n</font></span></div>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">4</span>月<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">24</span>日，县政协召开关于县自来水（甘泉水业）公司营运及收费情况听证问政会。县政协主席葛婷，副县长李德炳，副主席雷家兴、严嘉芬、赵季明、刘平出席会议。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">葛婷说，自<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2007</span>年企业改制以来，县自来水公司做了很多的工作，不仅妥善的处理了改制债务，还对基础设施建设加大了投入，对城区的管网进行了改造，在服务上下了真功夫，成绩值得肯定。她要求，下一步，自来水公司要加大企业内部管理，控制运行成本；要加大管网改造投入，特别是要有计划、有力度的对老城区管网进行改造，相关设备要及时更新；要提升服务质量和服务水平，加大宣传力度，宣传国家政策、标准、企业服务和企业文化，要让老百姓了解和支持自来水公司的发展。她强调，自来水公司要严格执行上级有关政策，自来水价格和报装开户要合理、公开，不能给企业和群众增加额外负担。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">李德炳说，自来水问题涉及民生，不仅仅是企业内部的问题，还是社会问题和政治问题，处理得不好就会影响稳定。他要求县住建局对自来水公司加强指导，对相关问题及时进行监督和管理；自来水公司也要千方百计提升服务质量，更好的为县域经济发展服务。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">针对县自来水公司报装开户价格较高，报价和市场价格相差较大；城区管网改造进度较慢，存在头痛医头脚痛医脚现象；部分职工服务态度较差等问题，县政协委员分别提出了各自的意见和建议。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">会前，政协委员一行察看了县自来水公司的取水点和石矶头水厂。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">县住建局局长尹彬生，县政协各委室负责人，及县政协委员何晓山、邹明、叶丛兵、刘再蓉、王俊、黄达文、刘红军、罗和荣、孔修直、王芳、李桂林、周双清、杨新、耿海军参加会议。</font></span></p>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2012-04-24/b89933cfaab46aeb2acc4d9207c084ca.jpg\\\\\" /><br />\r\n查看石叽头水厂<br />\r\n</font></span></div>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><o:p><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1523','6','熊铁山','中国嘉鱼网','<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2012-04-25/d1f6d90f13cfc39f5dd707ceb8485973.jpg\\\\\" /><br />\r\n查看华亿通橡胶有限公司建筑工地<br />\r\n</font></span></div>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">4</span>月<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">25</span>日，县政协主席葛婷到华亿通橡胶产业园督办项目建设进度。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">葛婷一行来到</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\">华亿通橡胶产业园施工现场，</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">实地查看了项目的建设进展，并听取该公司负责人的情况介绍，详细了解项目的进展、存在的问题及下一步工作计划等。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\">葛婷指出，各相关单位要多深入项目现场了解情况，抓好协调、督促，扎实推进项目建设；要切实履行牵头、协调、跟踪的责任，协助项目化解矛盾，努力提供全方位优质服务，尤其要加强协调沟通，对项目涉及的各种问题，要尽快为他们办理好相关手续，</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">全力促进项目快建设、早竣工、早投产。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">据悉，湖北华亿通橡胶有限公司是由上海华亿通实业有限公司在湖北投资兴办的一家新型橡胶加工企业即橡胶产业园。项目规划占地面积<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">1000</span>亩，总投资<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">8</span>亿元人民币，注册资本金为<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">5000</span>万元。项目分两期建设，首期投资<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2.8</span>亿元，建成后园区静脉产业链部分可实现产值<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">7.2</span>亿元，创利税<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2.2</span>亿元，项目全部建成投产后可创造产值<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">14</span>亿元。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">目前，该产业园正在进行车间和厂房的主体建设，整个基础设施建设正在有序推进，预计主体工程在<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">8</span>月底完工，首期工程在<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">9</span>月底可以正式投入生产。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1518','6','金家斌','中国嘉鱼网','<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><st1:chsdate w:st=\\\\\"on\\\\\" isrocdate=\\\\\"False\\\\\" islunardate=\\\\\"False\\\\\" day=\\\\\"23\\\\\" month=\\\\\"4\\\\\" year=\\\\\"2012\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">4</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">月</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">23</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">日</span></st1:chsdate><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">，市养老保险局局长胡程道一行来到县人社局，就我县养老保险经办工作进行专项调研。县人社局局长张海河，各养老保险经办机构负责人陪同调研。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">胡程道听取了我县各养老保险经办机构负责人汇报，并对养老保险经办工作进行了实地调研后，他高兴地说，此次调研是我市今年养老保险经办工作的重要工作，我县完成得非常好。他要求我县在下一步工作中宜稳中求进，重点做好城乡居民社会养老保险全履盖工作。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">据悉，这次调研的内容主要包括：对我县</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">2012</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">年企业退休人员调整待遇工作落实情况；养老保险基金审计检查工作情况；机关事业单位养老保险运行情况；城乡居民社会养老保险参保缴费、待遇发放、系统运用及数据上传情况等。</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1519','6','刘蒙','中国嘉鱼网','<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2012-04-24/3f65023c198870e6d31bc32c0ae93136.jpg\\\\\" /><br />\r\n</font></span></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">查看三乐泵站<br />\r\n</font></span></div>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">4</span>月<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">24</span>日，县委书记熊征宇、县委副书记李国光在县水利局干部陪同下，来到鱼岳镇、高铁岭镇、陆溪镇等地重点泵站、堤防，检查各镇汛前准备工作情况。县委办主任章斌参加检查。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">熊征宇一行先后来到城区排涝泵站、三湖连江进洪闸、三乐泵站、大岩湖、珍湖垸围堤、接里湖围堤、双合垸等地，实地察看并了解各泵站设备维护、堤防加固等情况。每年汛期，大岩湖水产养殖户与周边群众之间的排涝矛盾比较突出，为此高铁岭镇积极调解，劝导养殖户在大岩湖周边租了<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">60</span>亩的池塘专门提供汛期蓄水，保障今年防汛工作不再受矛盾影响。熊征宇对此表示赞赏，他要求养殖户能够充分考虑全局利益，与当地群众进一步协调好各项矛盾，将各方损失降到最小。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">在陆溪镇珍湖垸围堤的排涝泵站里，工作人员罗庆云正在认真检查泵站机组各个环节。陆溪镇负责人介绍说，罗庆云负责该镇三个重点泵站的维护<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">20</span>多年，对该镇各个泵站和堤防情况非常熟悉。熊征宇握着罗庆云的手，对他多年来的辛勤工作表示感谢，并向他详细了解了该镇近年来的防汛重点、难点问题。熊征宇说，这样的老专家对情况熟悉，经验丰富，水利部门及各镇要充分发挥好他们作用。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">熊征宇强调，汛期即将来临，各级各部门要牢牢把握防汛抗灾的主动权，进一步强化责任意识和忧患意识；及时掌握和了解水情、雨情监测，认真落实各级各类防汛预案，扎实做好防汛工程设施的检查和养护，加强防汛抢险物资的储备管理，做到有备无患，确保人民群众的生命财产安全。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">据了解，今年以来，我县立足于防大汛、抗大旱，从早、从紧、从实做好备汛备旱的各项工作，县水利部门已先后组织<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">6</span>次汛前检查，对辖内长江堤防、民堤民垸、内湖围堤、泵站等开展徒步检查；督促完成了大、中型排灌泵站维修与保养，<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">3</span>月底余码头泵站已开机灌溉，其它泵站可随时投入运行；对长江堤防仓库的防汛物料进行了清查与复核，现储备草袋<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">1.1</span>万条，编织袋<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">35</span>万条，彩条布<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">0.<st1:chmetcnv w:st=\\\\\"on\\\\\" unitname=\\\\\"米\\\\\" sourcevalue=\\\\\"90000\\\\\" hasspace=\\\\\"False\\\\\" negative=\\\\\"False\\\\\" numbertype=\\\\\"1\\\\\" tcsc=\\\\\"1\\\\\">9<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">万米</span></span></st1:chmetcnv><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">，铁丝0.5</span></span>吨，救生衣<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">270</span>件。<br />\r\n</font></span></p>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2012-04-24/9ba6bdd1de95a6b87230c8ca855e7d96.jpg\\\\\" /></font></span></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">查看高铁岭镇大岩湖</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><o:p><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\">&nbsp;</div>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1522','6','张旭','中国嘉鱼网','<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2012-04-25/7cee25ea2c1778a62d0e7c895c3ef520.jpg\\\\\" /><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2012-04-25/6fefe5b0b94619493aa6df44c2492bc7.jpg\\\\\" /><br />\r\n<span style=\\\\\"font-size: 16px\\\\\">全民阅读活动现场<br />\r\n</span></div>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\\\\\">&ldquo;让全民阅读之风吹遍南嘉的每一个角落！&rdquo;<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">4</span>月<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">25</span>日，嘉鱼县<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2012</span>年&ldquo;书香嘉鱼&middot;文化强县&rdquo;全民阅读活动启动仪式正式拉开了我县全民阅读活动的序幕。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\\\\\">据了解，在每年<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">4</span>月份的读书月活动中，集中启动&ldquo;书香嘉鱼&middot;文化强县&rdquo;全民阅读相关主题活动，已成为嘉鱼县的一个&ldquo;惯例&rdquo;。今年，我县将以&ldquo;学党史、知党情、跟党走&rdquo;学习教育活动，图书展销会，&ldquo;喜迎十八大、争创新业绩&rdquo;党史知识竞赛，&ldquo;阅读&middot;成长&rdquo;征文活动，网络读书活动，图书漂流活动，&ldquo;我读书，我快乐，我成长&rdquo;校园读书活动，图书馆亲子之旅活动，广泛开展书香机关、书香企业、书香校园、书香社区、书香村组、书香人家创建活动，青年演讲赛<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">10</span>项主题活动掀起全民阅读活动高潮，让南嘉大地充满&ldquo;思想的活力、知识的动力、文化的魅力&rdquo;。为认真开展好全民阅读活动，我县成立了县全民阅读活动领导小组，将<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">10</span>项主题活动时间细化到月份，责任落实到单位。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\\\\\">当天，活动共发放倡议书<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">1000</span>余份，为学校及社区捐赠图书<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2000</span>余册，图书现场展销吸引了一波又一波的购书、观展潮。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\\\\\">县委副书记李国光宣布嘉鱼县全民阅读活动正式启动，县委常委、宣传部长刘合权主持仪式，县领导李电波、饶自斌、雷家兴等出席活动。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1524','6','刘蒙','中国嘉鱼网','<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2012-04-25/9831f15a440085f21ddfaa32f13141eb.jpg\\\\\" /><br />\r\n</font></span></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">比赛现场<br />\r\n</font></span></div>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><st1:chsdate w:st=\\\\\"on\\\\\" isrocdate=\\\\\"False\\\\\" islunardate=\\\\\"False\\\\\" day=\\\\\"25\\\\\" month=\\\\\"4\\\\\" year=\\\\\"2012\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">4</span>月<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">25</span>日上午</st1:chsdate>，我县&ldquo;喜迎十八大，争创新业绩&rdquo;地税杯党史知识竞赛拉开帷幕，来自各镇、县直单位的<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">17</span>支代表队进行了预赛角逐，其中陆溪镇、新街镇、洲湾镇、人民医院、县委办、公安局<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">6</span>支代表队晋级<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">26</span>日举行的决赛。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">预赛分为上午乡镇专场和下午县直部门专场，每支代表队由<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">4</span>名队员组成，每支队伍需回答<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">4</span>道必答题，<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2</span>道共答题，随后进入到激烈的抢答题和风险题环节。其中，新街镇代表队队员全部为女同志，她们可谓巾帼不让须眉，在整场比赛中，所有题目均回答正确，没有出现一处失误，最终以乡镇专场第一名的成绩晋级决赛。县公安局代表队的警官们则以他们快捷的反映速度在抢答题中占据优势，最终以最高分<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">340</span>分晋级决赛。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"mso-spacerun: yes\\\\\">&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\">&ldquo;参加此次竞赛活动给我们提供了一次难得的学习机会，对我们个人的理论素质提高起到很好的作用。&rdquo;县委办代表队队员尹瑶说道，并希望以后这样的活动能经常举办。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\">26</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\">日举行的决赛除了预赛晋级的<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">6</span>支队伍外，还包括县地税局代表队，共<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">7</span>支队伍参加。</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></font>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1525','6','周艳','中国嘉鱼网','<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2012-04-26/d65cf6469b33b039dca4329ada612649.jpg\\\\\" /><br />\r\n<span style=\\\\\"font-size: 16px\\\\\">嘉鱼分会场现场</span></div>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><st1:chsdate w:st=\\\\\"on\\\\\" isrocdate=\\\\\"False\\\\\" islunardate=\\\\\"False\\\\\" day=\\\\\"25\\\\\" month=\\\\\"4\\\\\" year=\\\\\"2012\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">4</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">月</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">25</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">日</span></st1:chsdate><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">，省政府召开</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">2012</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">年度全省纠风工作暨政风行风民主评议工作电视电话会议，传达贯彻全国纠风工作会议精神，安排部署全省纠风工作。县委常委、常务副县长熊武华出席嘉鱼分会场会议。</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">会议充分肯定了</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">2011</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">年我省纠风工作取得的成效，并要求全省上下要清醒地看到，当前一些重点领域的不正之风仍比较突出，损害群众利益的行为时有发生，一些问题纠而复生、屡禁不止，纠风工作涉及领域越来越广，工作方式方法和体制机制亟待改革创新。</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">会议强调，今年的纠风工作要突出重点，切实解决损害群众利益的突出问题，重点抓好商业银行、大型零售企业及涉农、物流、通信、教育领域乱收费问题治理，整治医药购销和医疗服务中存在的突出问题，开展规范党政机关举办节庆活动等专项纠风工作。要进一步深化民主评议政风行风工作，坚持以问题为导向，把握好自查自纠和问题整改两个关键环节，在行评结果运用上加大改革创新力度。要在制度建设上下工夫，从源头上防治不正之风，以政风行风建设的实际成效，更好地服务跨越式发展大局。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">会议要求，各地各部门把纠风和政风行风评议工作放在更突出的位置，迅速对今年的纠风工作任务进行分解落实，形成一级抓一级、层层抓落实的工作格局，以实际工作成效取信于民，以新的成绩迎接党的十八大胜利召开。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\" size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>');");
